<strong><span style="color: rgb(65, 152, 0);">Facilities at startpoint:</span></strong><span style="color: rgb(105, 105, 105);">Pub, Cafe, Car Park, Restaurant, Accomodation, Bus Stop, National Park Information, Shop, Toilets, Post Office</span></span></span></div>
